title: Pato-ko Ikkimasu!
original_name: パト娘 いっきまーす！
sinopse:
In the town with a lighthouse, Inubosaki, the police patrol division's new recruit, Kurumi, and the talking middle-aged police-car-dog No.1 are on the case! Everyday, they somewhat protect the peace of Inubosaki, but is it okay to leave it up to the rambunctious duo? The new sensation that is the cute, slice-of-life short comedy is here!

(Source: MangaBox)
